Package com.IGallinari.LastGame.service.API_to_DB.HandleJSON

Class PlayersHandler

java.lang.Object
com.IGallinari.LastGame.service.API_to_DB.HandleJSON.PlayersHandler
All Implemented Interfaces:
Handler
@Service public class PlayersHandler extends Object implements Handler
Service class to handle the processing of player data received in JSON format. This class is responsible for parsing the JSON data, extracting relevant player information, and persisting it into the database using PlayerRepository and PlayerTeamRepository.
